tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE location_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  latitude DECIMAL,
  longitude DECIMAL,
  address VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE network_coverage (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    latitude DECIMAL(9,6),
    longitude DECIMAL(9,6),
    cell_id INT,
    signal_strength INT
);

CREATE TABLE coverage_areas (
    coverage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_id INT,
    location_id INT,
    coverage_range FLOAT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_network
        FOREIGN KEY (network_id)
        REFERENCES networks(network_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_location
        FOREIGN KEY (location_id)
        REFERENCES locations(location_id)
);

CREATE TABLE signal_strength (
    signal_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    coverage_id INT,
    signal_value INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_coverage
        FOREIGN KEY (coverage_id)
        REFERENCES coverage_areas(coverage_id)
);

CREATE TABLE network_coverage (
    coverage_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    location_id UUID,
    operator VARCHAR(50),
    technology VARCHAR(50),
    coverage_type VARCHAR(50),
    coverage_area FLOAT
);
